reviewText: John Witherspoon has been funny for years and this stand up comedy dvd proves that even more.  I got a chance to catch this stand up on HBO a few months back and i was rolling with laughter.  I will definitely be adding this to my archives of dvd collections.  John Witherspoon is just too damn funny.  Bang, bang, bang, bang!
summary: Hooray for the native Detroit comedian!
Title: John Witherspoon: You Got to Coordinate

reviewText: Man he finally dropped a stand up dvd. I was so glad when i tracked this down. it was way funny as I expected. John is a classic and I was so glad they decidded to drop this one.
Title: John Witherspoon: You Got to Coordinate

reviewText: I caught this set on cable last week and I was in tears from laughing so hard! This is a really funny set running a little under an hour with no dead spots! One of the best I've seen in a long while. I think it would go over better with the over 30's crowd. I ended up buying this a few days ago.
summary: HYSTERICAL! ONE OF THE BEST STAND UPS I'VE SEEN IN A LONG TIME!
Title: John Witherspoon: You Got to Coordinate

reviewText: This rountine started out kind of slow.  I didn't think he was funny in the first half hour of the show.  He quickly got funny after that and kept me laughing for the rest of the movie.  If you don't mind a slow start its worth the price of the DVD to get it.
Title: John Witherspoon: You Got to Coordinate

reviewText: I caught this on Showtime last night.  I hadn't laughed so hard in a very long time!  This man is just a riot!  There really isn't much else I can say.  I'm glad there's a DVD for this.  I'll be picking it up very soon!  If you like to laugh, don't even think about it, just get this.  You won't be disappointed!
Title: John Witherspoon: You Got to Coordinate
